data.title: ‘Dancing With the Stars’: A Look Back at Each Season’s Cast (Photos)
data.meta_description: The dancing competition featured singers, actors, dancers, Olympians and many more who each competed for the acclaimed Mirror Ball trophy through the past 10 years.
data.text:
Season 1

Cast (celebrity and pro partner): Trista Sutter and Louis van Amstel, Evander Holyfield and Edyta Sliwinska, Rachel Hunter and Jonathan Roberts, Joey McIntyre and Ashly DelGrosso, John O'Hurley and Charlotte Jorgensen, Kelly Monaco and Alec Mazo.

Hosts: Tom Bergeron and Lisa Canning

Winners: Kelly Monaco and Alec Mazo
